# GEOFF Local Model Modelfiles (Fallback)
#
# These Modelfiles are used if you want to build models from GGUF files
# downloaded directly from HuggingFace, instead of using `ollama pull`.
#
# The primary install method is `ollama pull` with identity verification
# (see manifest.toml). These Modelfiles are provided as a fallback for
# air-gapped environments or custom builds.
#
# To use:
#   1. Download the GGUF from the HuggingFace repo listed in manifest.toml
#   2. Place it in this directory
#   3. Run: ollama create <model-name> -f <modelfile>

